# billing service

Module: `github.com/dobriygolang/project-nordly/services/billing`. Work from service root only.

## Layers

```
cmd/billing/app/run.go          → DI
internal/app/api/billing/       → gRPC/HTTP transport
internal/billing/               → model, repository, service, usecases
internal/adapter/identity/      → identity token validation
```

HTTP `:8085`, gRPC `:9095`. **Prod service** — plans, entitlements, usage quotas, Tribute webhooks.
